  "texts": [
    "ℎ 𝑡 = 𝑜 𝑡 * tanh(𝐶 𝑡)(6) RESULTS AND DISCUSSIONThe simulation phase begins by collecting data.",
    "This study employed data extracted from video comments on YouTube on the 2024 presidential election.",
    "Furthermore, the data pre-processing phase was carried out, which involved performing data purification and applying one-hot encoding.",
    "Later on, BERT is used to represent the data.",
    "The resulting representation results are then used as input for doing sentiment analysis utilizing the CNN, LSTM, CNN-LSTM, and LSTM-CNN models."
  ]
